            <h1 class="fw-bold mb-3">Health Topics API</h1>
            <p class="lead">Query over 2,000 structured health topics through a simple REST API. Every topic is ICD-10 classified, typed, and sourced from authoritative medical references.</p>

            <a href="/register" class="btn btn-primary mt-2 mb-4">Get a free API key</a>

            <hr>

            <h2 class="fw-semibold">What Health Topic Data Is Available?</h2>
            <p>The Meducate health topics API provides access to a structured dataset of medical conditions, diseases, drugs, symptoms, procedures, and wellness topics. The dataset covers the full scope of the MedlinePlus health topic library — over 2,000 topics spanning every major area of medicine.</p>
            <p>Each health topic in the API includes:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Name</strong> — the canonical topic name</li>
                <li><strong>Description</strong> — a structured summary synthesised from authoritative sources</li>
                <li><strong>Type</strong> — classification of the topic kind: Disease, Drug, Procedure, Symptom, Condition, or Wellness</li>
                <li><strong>ICD-10 category</strong> — the ICD-10 chapter the topic belongs to (e.g. Respiratory System, Mental & Behavioral, Drugs & Medications)</li>
            </ul>

            <hr>

            <h2 class="fw-semibold">Topic Types Covered</h2>

            <h3 class="fw-semibold mt-3">Diseases & Conditions</h3>
            <p>The largest category. Covers chronic conditions (diabetes, hypertension, asthma), acute diseases (pneumonia, appendicitis), infectious diseases (influenza, HIV), and rare conditions. Each is classified by ICD-10 body system or condition category.</p>

            <h3 class="fw-semibold mt-3">Drugs & Medications</h3>
            <p>Common prescription and over-the-counter medications, including their uses, classifications, and related conditions. Mapped to the Drugs & Medications ICD-10 category for consistent filtering.</p>

            <h3 class="fw-semibold mt-3">Medical Procedures</h3>
            <p>Surgical procedures, diagnostic tests, and medical interventions. Useful for building procedure lookup tools, pre-procedure patient education content, or billing assistance features.</p>

            <h3 class="fw-semibold mt-3">Symptoms</h3>
            <p>Common patient-reported symptoms classified by body system. Useful as input for symptom checker logic or triage flow classification.</p>

            <h3 class="fw-semibold mt-3">Wellness & Preventive Care</h3>
            <p>Topics covering nutrition, mental health, preventive care, and general wellness — ideal for consumer-facing health apps and patient engagement platforms.</p>

            <h3 class="fw-semibold mt-3">Pediatric Health</h3>
            <p>Conditions, developmental milestones, and health topics specific to children and adolescents, classified under the Pediatric Health category.</p>

            <hr>

            <h2 class="fw-semibold">ICD-10 Category Coverage</h2>
            <p>Every topic is assigned to one of 24 ICD-10 aligned categories:</p>
